Roukaya Moussa Mahamane (amụrụ ya na 13 Jenụwarị 1997 na Niamey) bụ onye Naijiria na-egwu mmiri. O sonyere na asọmpi mita nke iri ise nke ụmụ nwanyị na 2016 Summer Olympics, ebe ọ nọ n'ọnọdụ nke onye nke mmadụ iri asatọ na atọ na oge nke 36.50 sekọnd, ihe ndekọ mba. Ọ gakwaghị n'ihu na ọkara ikpeazụ.
N'afọ 2019, ọ nọchitere anya Niger na World Aquatics Championships nke e mere na Gwangju, South Korea
O sonyere na asọmpi mita iri is nke ụmụ nwanyị na otu narị nke ụmụ nwanyị. N'ihe omume abụọ ahụ, ọ gara n'ihu ịsọ mpi na ọkara ikpeazụ.
O sonyere na asọmpi mita 50 nke ụmụ nwanyị na 2020 Summer Olympics.
Ọ nọchitere anya Niger na 2022 World Aquatics Championships nke e mere na Budapest, Hungary. O sonyere na asọmpi mita 50 nke ụmụ nwanyị na 100 nke ụmụ nwanyị.
